# output.co: flow definitions for the L4 output rail.
#
# `self_check_output` is already declared in config.yml's
# rails.output.flows, so no custom flow is needed here unless we want
# to override the default `define bot refuse to respond` from input.co.
#
# Keep this file present so NeMo's `RailsConfig.from_path` finds it and
# the L2/L3 layer is recognised as configured (security review SC-7).
